<bibRefCitation author="CHAN T. - Y. &amp; YU H. - P." box="[380,575,1618,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="504" pagination="121 - 127" refId="ref134567" refString="CHAN T. - Y. &amp; YU H. - P. 1992. - Scyllarus formosanus, a new slipper lobster (Decapoda, Scyllaridae) from Taiwan. Crustaceana 62 (2): 121 - 127, pls 1, 2." type="book chapter" year="1992">Chan &amp; Yu, 1992</bibRefCitation>
